    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable ride that won't let you down? This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and shows it! You'll find a clean, well-maintained interior and an exterior that presents nicely with only minor signs of normal use. Mechanically, it runs great and is ready to hit the road without any major concerns. A few small cosmetic imperfections remind you this is a real-world vehicle, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. If you're looking for a dependable car that offers solid value, this one is well worth a look!",
