    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\u2728 Mint Condition & Absolutely Stunning \u2014 A Used Car That Feels Brand New! \u2728 This vehicle is in exceptional mint condition \u2014 meticulously cared for and showing virtually no signs of wear inside or out! The exterior gleams with a flawless finish, free of scratches, dents, or blemishes, while the interior is immaculate \u2014 clean, fresh, and beautifully preserved. Every system runs perfectly, and the drive feels smooth, responsive, and confidence-inspiring. If you've been searching for a used car that truly delivers a like-new experience, this is the one. Don't miss your chance to own a genuine mint-condition gem! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly exceptional, mint condition at a price of $46,000. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 paint is deep, vibrant, and free of scratches, scuffs, dents, or any blemishes whatsoever. The interior is equally impressive, showing no signs of wear: seats, carpets, dashboard, and all trim pieces look and feel as if they just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in top-notch shape \u2014 all systems function perfectly, with no warning lights, no unusual noises, and no deferred maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that genuinely rivals a new car in presentation and reliability. A serious buyer who wants the best will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in fair condition, and that is an honest and straightforward assessment. The exterior shows visible signs of use \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some paint fading in spots, and possibly a minor dent or two. The interior is functional but worn, with scuffs on surfaces and some wear on the upholstery consistent with regular daily driving. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a solid option for a buyer who wants reliable basic transportation and is comfortable handling minor cosmetic and maintenance items themselves. No major mechanical surprises are being hidden here \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car, and it is genuinely one of the finest examples you will find on the used market. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the original paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. All body panels are perfectly aligned, trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is crystal clear throughout. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 seats show no wear, fading, or staining, the dashboard and door panels are free of cracks or scuffs, and every surface presents as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health: the engine starts immediately, runs smoothly, and pulls strongly through all gears. All systems \u2014 climate control, electronics, safety features, and infotainment \u2014 function perfectly. Service history is clean and up to date. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic touch-ups, no surprises. What you see is exactly what you get, and what you get is exceptional.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
